      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Reality systems have two languages installed.
To change a language:<ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Hash key</b> to enter the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">User stack</b>. </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Use the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Arrow keys</b> to navigate to the current language.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">For the second language: </b>Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Clock/number 1
key</b> to activate the second language.</p>
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">For the first language: </b>Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Star/number 0 key</b> to activate the first language.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Back key</b> or wait 30 seconds to exit the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">User stack</b>.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </p>
         </sectiondiv>
